  "original_title": "\u0b87\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bb2 \u0bae\u0bbe\u0b95\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bb4\u0bc8  \u0baa\u0bc6\u0baf\u0bcd\u0baf\u0bb2\u0bbe\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Rain may occur in many provinces today",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "Sabaragamuwa province and Nuwara Eliya and Kandy districts are likely to experience occasional rain.",
        "Upper and North-West Provinces and Galle and Matara districts will experience several spells of rain.",
        "Occasional gusty winds (40-50 km/h) are expected in the western slopes of Central Highlands and Southern Province.",
        "Temporarily gusty winds may occur in these areas during periods of thundershowers. The public is advised to take necessary precautions to minimize the damage caused by lightning strikes.",
        "Rain or thundershowers are expected at many places along coastal areas from Puttalam through Colombo and Galle to Ambantota.",
        "Wind will be blowing from West to Southwest direction with wind speed of 30-40 kmph. Wind speed may increase to 50-60 kmph over coastal areas from Puttalam to Pottuvil through Colombo, Galle and Ambantota.",
        "The sea surface from Puttalam through Colombo, Galle and Ambantota to Pottuvil is turbulent. Other seas surrounding the country are expected to be moderate.",
        "Waves (about 2.5 \u2013 3.0 m) may increase in offshore areas from Puttalam to Pottuvil through Colombo, Galle and Ambantota.",
        "The navy and fishing communities engaged in fishing and naval activities in the waters from Puttalam to Pottu through Colombo, Galle and Ambandottai have been requested to be vigilant in this regard."
      ],
